refsection.para:
Other parameters of the acquisition are set to:

        First frame equals to 1: use btkSetFirstFrame to modify it ;
        Points' frequency equals to 0: use btkSetFrequency to modify it ;
        Points' units set to "mm", "deg", "N", "Nmm", "W", "" for markers, angles, forces, moments, powers and scalars respectively. Use btkSetPointUnit to modify them ;
        Analogs' frequency equals to 0. Updated when the points' frequency is ;
        Analog channel resolution sets to 12 bits: use btkSetAnalogResolution to modify it.

refsection.programlisting:
// 10 points, 1000 frames and no analog channels.
h = btkNewAcquisition(10, 1000)
// 10 points, 1000 frames and 12 analog channels with the same number of frames.
h = btkNewAcquisition(10, 1000, 12)
// 10 points, 1000 frames and 12 analog channels with a number of frames  equals to 2 times the number of frames for the points.
h = btkNewAcquisition(10, 1000, 12, 2)
